trans-unit.source: Provides a standard set of component-related commands, which have predefined key input gestures and <see cref="P:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text" /> properties.
trans-unit.target: Fornece um conjunto padrão de comandos relacionados ao componente, que tem gestos de entrada chave predefinidos e propriedades <see cref="P:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text" />.

trans-unit.source: The commands in the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands> class and commands in the other command library classes, such as <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>, are intended to represent a set of common commands that application programmers encounter frequently.
trans-unit.target: Os comandos de <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands> classe e comandos no outro comando classes de biblioteca, tais como <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands> e <xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>, serve para representar um conjunto de comandos comuns que os programadores de aplicativos com frequência encontram.

trans-unit.source: The commands only represent the instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> and not the implementation logic for the command.
trans-unit.target: Os comandos representam apenas a instância das <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> e não a lógica de implementação do comando.

trans-unit.source: The implementation logic is bound to the command via a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.
trans-unit.target: A lógica de implementação é associada ao comando por meio de um <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> command is executed on a control (the command target), the logic that performs the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> command may not be provided by the command target, so the application writer is responsible for writing the logic that determines how the command target handles the command.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, se o <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> comando é executado em um controle (o destino do comando), a lógica que executa o <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> comando não pode ser fornecido pelo destino de comando, portanto o gravador de aplicativos é responsável por gravar a lógica que determina como o destino do comando lida com o comando.

trans-unit.source: Many controls do provide implementation logic, though, for many of the commands in the command library.
trans-unit.target: Muitos controles fornecer lógica de implementação, no entanto, para muitos dos comandos na biblioteca de comandos.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> class provides logic for the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A> command, and <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> command.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> classe fornece lógica para o <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A> comando <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A> comando, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A> comando, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A> comando, e <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> comando.

trans-unit.source: See the class documentation for particular control classes for more information.
trans-unit.target: Consulte a documentação da classe para classes de controle específico para obter mais informações.

trans-unit.source: For more information on commands and commanding, see [Commanding Overview](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/commanding-overview.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre comandos e comandos, consulte [visão geral do comando](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/commanding-overview.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets the value that represents the Extend Selection Down command.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor que representa o comando Estender Seleção para Baixo.

trans-unit.source: This command indicates the intention to extend the selection downward.
trans-unit.target: Este comando indica a intenção de estender a seleção para baixo.

trans-unit.source: There is not necessarily an actual implementation responding to the command on any given object; in many cases the implementation in response to that command is the responsibility of the application writer.
trans-unit.target: Não há necessariamente uma implementação real responder ao comando de qualquer objeto especificado; em muitos casos, a implementação em resposta a esse comando é responsabilidade do gravador de aplicativos.
